

Estimate
- A proposal of work to be done for a client to sign off
- Could consist of various types of work
- one or more Work Items
- Grand total rolled up from Work Items

Work Item
- Related set of tasks to be done
- Has one or more Materials and/or People
- recurring details (weekly, bi-weekly, monthly, etc)
- Tax %
- Subtotal rolled up from Materials and People

Job
- When a Work Item is assigned to a Crew and put into a Schedule
- Breaks down a Work Items into Activities

Crew
- One or more Employees
- Closely match the People role in Work Item

Schedule
- Block of times when Activities will be done
- Might not be contiguous

Activity
- Each Job can have one or more activities
- A Job is complete when all the activities are done

Invoice
- one or more completed Jobs
